---

<Layout
  description="Docker vs serverless in 2025. Containers aren't dead but do you actually need them? A pragmatic take on when to use what."
  title="Do You Actually Need Docker? A Pragmatic Take on Containers vs Serverless · Blog · Aidxn Design"
>

    <SlotBlog>
      <Fragment slot="category">
        Tech News
      </Fragment>
      <Fragment slot="title">
        Do You Actually Need Docker? A Pragmatic Take on Containers vs Serverless
      </Fragment>

      <Fragment slot="cover">
        <div class="w-full h-48 rounded bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-600/20 to-cyan-500/20 flex items-center justify-center">
          <span class="text-4xl">&#128051;</span>
        </div>
